data.description: Stunning 180 degree views from this custom built home! Master suite to die for, his & her offices or home gym. Huge walk in closet with builts ins, no need for dressers! Gorgeous custom hardwood flooring, massive rock fireplace. Open floor plan in main living to kitchen and two sunrooms with extensive views! One of a kind floor plan to take advantage of every view of the Sierra's. Full privacy with no neighbors looking in.
